 the table centered. We can use the shorthand property margin and set it to auto for aligning the table at the center rather than using the margin-left and margin-right property.\']','[\'<!DOCTYPE>\', \'<html>\', \'<style>\', \'table, th, td {\', \'border: 1px solid black;\', \'margin-left: auto;\', \'margin-right: auto;\', \'border-collapse: collapse;\', \'width: 500px;\', \'text-align: center;\', \'font-size: 20px;\', \'</style>\', \'</head>\', \'<body>\', \'<table>\', \'<th>First_Name</th>\', \'<th>Last_Name</th>\', \'<th>Subject</th>\', \'<th>Marks</th>\', \'</tr>\', \'<td>James</td><td>Gosling</td><td>Maths</td><td>92</td>\', \'</tr>\', \'<td>Alan</td><td>Rickman</td><td>Maths</td><td>89</td>\', \'</tr>\', \'<td>Sam</td><td>Mendes</td><td>Maths</td><td>82</td>\', \'</tr>\', \'</table>\', \'</body>\', \'</html>\']','[]','[]','[]'),(140,'[\'How to center text in CSS?\']','[\'In HTML, the <center> tag is used to center an element. The correct and modern way to center text is by using the CSS properties. It can be of the easiest task, but when we have more elements or large code, it can sometimes be confusing. The text-align property in CSS is responsible for the alignment of the text. This CSS property is used to set the horizontal alignment of a table-cell box or the block element. It is similar to the vertical-align property but in the horizontal direction.\']','[\'https://www.javatpoint.com/how-to-add-background-image-in-css\', \'https://www.javatpoint.com/how-to-center-a-table-in-css\', \'https://www.javatpoint.com/https://www.javatpoint.com/css-tutorial\', \'https://www.javatpoint.com/https://www.javatpoint.com/oprweb/test.jsp?filename=HowtocentertextinCSS1\', \'https://www.javatpoint.com/how-to-add-background-image-in-css\', \'https://www.javatpoint.com/how-to-center-a-table-in-css\', \'https://www.javatpoint.com/how-to-add-background-image-in-css\']','[\'https://static.javatpoint.com/csspages/images/how-to-center-text-in-css1.png\']','[]','[]','[\'Syntax\', \'Example\']','[]','[\'So, the text-align: center; is used for aligning the text to the center.\']','[\'Although the text-align property includes values like justify, center, right, left, initial, inherit, but using the center value, we can align the text to the center.\']','[]','[\'text-align: center;\', \'<html>\', \'<head>\', \'</head>\', \'<style>\', \'text-align: center;\', \'font-size: 25px;\', \'color: blue;\', \'</style>\', \'<body>\', \'<h1>Example of text-align: center; </h1>\', \'\', \'<h2>\', \'text-align: center;\', \'</h2>\', \'<div>\', \'<p>Hello World</p>\', \'<p> Welcome to the javaTpoint.com </p>\', \'</div>\', \'</body>\', \'</html>\']','[]','[]','[]'),(141,'[\'How to add background image in CSS?\']','[\'The background-image property in CSS is used to set an image as the background of an element. Using this CSS property, we can set one or more than one background image for an element.\']','[\'https://www.javatpoint.com/how-to-vertically-align-text-with-css\', \'https://www.javatpoint.com/how-to-center-text-in-css\', \'https://www.javatpoint.com/https://www.javatpoint.com/url-full-form\', \'https://www.javatpoint.com/https://www.javatpoint.com/oprweb/test.jsp?filename=HowtoaddbackgroundimageinCSS1\', \'https://www.javatpoint.com/https://www.javatpoint.com/oprweb/test.jsp?filename=HowtoaddbackgroundimageinCSS2\', \'https://www.javatpoint.com/https://www.javatpoint.com/oprweb/test.jsp?filename=HowtoaddbackgroundimageinCSS3\', \'https://www.javatpoint.com/how-to-vertically-align-text-with-css\', \'https://www.javatpoint.com/how-to-center-text-in-css\', \'https://www.javatpoint.com/how-to-vertically-align-text-with-css\']','[\'https://static.javatpoint.com/csspages/images/how-to-add-background-image-in-css1.png\', \'https://static.javatpoint.com/csspages/images/how-to-add-background-image-in-css2.png\', \'https://static.javatpoint.com/csspages/images/how-to-add-background-image-in-css3.png\']','[]','[]','[\'Syntax\', \'Values\', \'Example\', \'Example\', \'Example\']','[]','[\'url(): It is the URL to the image. We can separate the URLs by a comma if we want to specify more than one image.\']','[]','[\'By default, the image is positioned at the top-left corner of an element and repeated both horizontally as well as vertically. The background image should be chosen according to the text color. The bad combination of text and background image may be a cause of poorly designed and not readable webpage.\', \"The url() value of this property allows us to include a file path to any image. It will show the element\'s background. We can use multiple images or a mixture of gradients and images for the background. If the background-image is failed to load or if we are using the gradients, but they are not supported on the corresponding browser then, we can use the fallback value (the value used as the substitution) as the background color of the element.\"]','[\'background-image: url();\', \'<!DOCTYPE html>\', \'<html>\', \'<head>\', \'<style>\', \'body {\', \'background-image: url(\"cat.png\");\', \'background-color: lightgray;\', \'</style>\', \'</head>\', \'<body>\', \'</body>\', \'</html>\', \'<!DOCTYPE html>\', \'<html>\', \'<head>\', \'<style>\', \'body {\', \'height: 200px;\', \'background-color: #cccccc;\', \'background-image: radial-gradient(red, green, yellow); }\', \'</style>\', \'</head>\', \'<body>\', \'</body>\', \'</html>\', \'<!DOCTYPE html>\', \'<html>\', \'<head>\', \'<style>\', \'body {\', \'height: 200px;\', \'background-color: #cccccc;\', \'background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 255, 0.5),rgba(255, 255, 0, 0.5)), url(\"lion.png\");\', \'</style>\', \'</head>\', \'<body>\', \'</body>\', \'</html>\']','[]','[]','[]'),(142,'[\'How to vertically align text with CSS?\']','[\'The vertical-align property in CSS is used to define the vertical alignment of an inline or table-cell box. It is one of the self-explanatory properties of CSS.\']','[\'https://www.javatpoint.com/how-to-underline-text-in-css\', \'